@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@workflowId = webhook-trigger-workflow

### 1. WEBHOOK 시작 workflow 저장
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workflows
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "{{workflowId}}",
  "name": "Webhook Trigger Workflow",
  "version": 1,
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "node_start",
      "name": "Webhook Start",
      "type": "START",
      "params": {},
      "metadata": {
        "triggerType": "WEBHOOK",
        "webhookToken": "secret-123"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "node_done",
      "name": "Done",
      "type": "END",
      "params": {
        "name": "Triggered from webhook"
      }
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "node_start": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "nodeId": "node_done",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    }
  }
}

### 2. webhook 호출로 workflow 실행
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/triggers/webhooks/{{workflowId}}?token=secret-123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "requestId": "webhook-001",
  "payload": "hello webhook"
}

> {% client.global.set("webhookExecutionId", response.body.executionId); %}

### 3. 실행 상태 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/executions/{{webhookExecutionId}}

### 4. 노드 실행 이력 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/executions/{{webhookExecutionId}}/nodes
